headline: Coinbase Launches Platform for Digital Token Offerings
summary: Coinbase Global  is launching a new platform to allow individual investors to purchase digital tokens before they are listed on its exchange.  Coinbase will host about one token sale a month on its new platform, which will use an algorithm to determine how tokens are allocated to investors.  Following this period, an algorithm will distribute the tokens, aiming for broad and equitable allocation, Coinbase said.
